  :markdown
    **Example 1** Simple mixins:
    
        a.twitter
          +sprite-img("icons-32.png", 1)
        a.facebook
          +sprite-img("icons-32png", 2)
    
    **Example 2** Sharing a common base:
    
        a
          +sprite-background("icons-32.png")
          a.twitter
            +sprite-column(1)
          a.facebook
            +sprite-row(2)
  